1.2 Distrebution

1.2.1 Binomial Distribution

n k

  • \(X \sim Bin(n,p)\) X

  • \(\mu = np\)

  • \(\sigma^2 = np(1-p)\)

  • \(P(k) = P(X = k) = {n \choose k} p^k(1-p)^{n-k}\)
